info.description:
itk-parabolicmorphology provides mathematical morphological erosion and dilation filters using parabolic structuring functions.
Please refer to:
R. Beare, "Morphology with parabolic structuring elements.", Insight Journal, January-June 2008, https://hdl.handle.net/1926/1370.
info.name: itk-parabolicmorphology
info.summary: ITK classes for mathematical morphology using parabolic structuring functions
